trans-unit.source: Abstract class that, when implemented, defines an animation segment with its own target value and interpolation method for a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames" />.
trans-unit.target: 實作時，以自己的目標值和 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames" /> 的插補方法定義動畫區段的抽象類別。

trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame" /> 類別的新執行個體，這個執行個體具有指定的目標 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame.Value" /> 和 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame.KeyTime" />。

trans-unit.source: The value to animate from.
trans-unit.target: 要建立動畫的來源值。

trans-unit.source: A value between 0.0 and 1.0, inclusive, that specifies the percentage of time that has elapsed for this key frame.
trans-unit.target: 介於 0.0 和 1.0 (含) 之間的值，指定這個主要畫面格經過的時間百分比。

trans-unit.source: Returns the interpolated value of a specific key frame at the progress increment provided.
trans-unit.target: 傳回在提供漸次累加時，特定主要畫面格的插補值。

trans-unit.source: The output value of this key frame given the specified base value and progress.
trans-unit.target: 在指定基底值和漸次累加時，這個主要畫面格的輸出值。

trans-unit.source: The base value is typically the initial value of the property being animated or the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BooleanKeyFrame.Value%2A> of the previous key frame.
trans-unit.target: 基底值通常是正在顯示動畫之屬性的初始值或<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BooleanKeyFrame.Value%2A>先前的主要畫面格。

trans-unit.source: Most implementations will return the value of `baseValue` when `keyFrameProgress` is 0.0.
trans-unit.target: 大部分的實作會傳回值的`baseValue`時`keyFrameProgress`為 0.0。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if <paramref name="keyFrameProgress" /> is not between 0.0 and 1.0, inclusive.
trans-unit.target: 當 <paramref name="keyFrameProgress" /> 不在 0.0 和 1.0 (含) 之間時發生。

trans-unit.source: The value to animate from; typically the value of the previous key frame.
trans-unit.target: 要建立動畫的來源值，通常是上一個主要畫面格的值。

trans-unit.source: A value between 0.0 and 1.0, inclusive, that specifies the percentage of time that has elapsed for this key frame.
trans-unit.target: 介於 0.0 和 1.0 (含) 之間的值，指定這個主要畫面格經過的時間百分比。

trans-unit.source: Calculates the value of a key frame at the progress increment provided.
trans-unit.target: 計算在提供漸次累加時，主要畫面格的值。

trans-unit.source: The output value of this key frame given the specified base value and progress.
trans-unit.target: 在指定基底值和漸次累加時，這個主要畫面格的輸出值。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the time at which the key frame's target <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame.Value" /> should be reached.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定應該到達主要畫面格之目標 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame.Value" /> 的時間。

trans-unit.source: The time at which the key frame's current value should be equal to its <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame.Value" /> property.
trans-unit.target: 主要畫面格之目前值的時間應該等於其 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame.Value" /> 屬性。

trans-unit.source: The default value is <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeyTime.Uniform" />.
trans-unit.target: 預設值是 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeyTime.Uniform" />。
